  "content": "<p></p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/584850283\" class=\"internal\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/58</span><span class=\"invisible\">4850283</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p data-pid=\"ray2YbkA\">刚来的请先从前文看起</p><p data-pid=\"Z9XFwHhC\">步骤一：打开分享给你的文件，点击发送给朋友</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b8ba8b292475f9bd212dde4d8203cb2f_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2310\" data-size=\"small\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-d765e88e2bd55e600d01fe8136ebbabd\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b8ba8b292475f9bd212dde4d8203cb2f_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"9purRkOX\">步骤二：发送给文件传输助手或其他朋友都行（不从自己发出的小程序中点投诉的话，是找不到提取码的；并且要在电脑端进行微信投诉后复制链接，手机端也是找不到的。）</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-61721d8e6095523600573134e13014aa_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"594\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-dc7f85c89aa3315eb295db7747e43a44\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"594\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-61721d8e6095523600573134e13014aa_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Y8jmS-2x\">在微信电脑端点开小程序，点击右上角三点，反馈与投诉</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-943f516497d9f78bf6efba947fbfa308_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"636\" data-rawheight=\"1168\" data-size=\"small\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-e16606ccd8e35d1c29bed970a00f59d5\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"636\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-943f516497d9f78bf6efba947fbfa308_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"hPlS0JO4\">步骤三：点击复制链接</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e9cc28f13a78bd33eae37b7585f0315b_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"955\" data-rawheight=\"1141\" data-size=\"small\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-f5aa18b0985895b2ccdb0a0321810da5\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"955\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e9cc28f13a78bd33eae37b7585f0315b_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"hvGmd7QW\">步骤四：把复制的链接粘贴出来，pwd=后面的四位数就是提取码了。细心的同学还能发现pwd前面是之前复制的网站地址</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-adcdd5eadd4e4d37ccb57ebecd9076ad_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"316\" data-rawheight=\"361\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-d8e540404dc3cafb89c4dead23488da7\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"316\"/></figure><p></p>",
